{"kanda":6,"sarga":98,"description":"","verses":[{"v":1,"dev":"हन्यमानेबलेतूर्णमन्योन्यंतेमहामृथे ।सरसीवमहाघर्मेसोपक्षीणेबभूवतुः","trans":"In the major conflict, each one destroying the other army, it seemed like the midsummer lakes totally lost its water.","words":[{"d":"महामृथे","m":"in the major conflict"},{"d":"अन्योन्यम्","m":"one another"},{"d":"हन्यमाने","m":"destroying"},{"d":"बले","m":"army"},{"d":"महाघर्मे","m":"midsummer"},{"d":"सरसीव","m":"lakes"},{"d":"तूर्णम्","m":"totally"},{"d":"सोपक्षीणे","m":"water goes down"},{"d":"बभूवतुः","m":"seemed"}]},{"v":2,"dev":"स्वबलस्यविघातेनविरूपाक्ष्वधेन च ।बभूवद्विगुणंक्रुद्धोरावणोराक्षसाधिपः","trans":"The Lord of Rakshasas, Ravana, became doubly angry by the destruction of his army and fall of Virupaksha.","words":[{"d":"राक्षसाधिपः","m":"Lord of Rakshasas"},{"d":"रावणः","m":"Ravana"},{"d":"स्वबलस्य","m":"his army"},{"d":"घातेन","m":"destruction"},{"d":"विरूपाक्ष्वधेन च","m":"fall of Virupaksha"},{"d":"द्विगुणम्","m":"doubly"},{"d":"क्रुद्धः","m":"angry"},{"d":"बभूव","m":"became"}]},{"v":3,"dev":"प्रक्षीणंतुबलंदृष्टवावध्यमानंवलीमुखैः ।बभूवास्यव्यथायुद्धेप्रेक्ष्यदैवविपर्ययम्","trans":"Rakshasa's army was killed by Vanaras and drastically reduced. Seeing the adversary of God's grace, Ravana was agonized on witnessing it.","words":[{"d":"युद्धे","m":"in war"},{"d":"वलीमुखैः","m":"by the Vanaras"},{"d":"वध्यमानम्","m":"killed"},{"d":"प्रक्षीणम्","m":"highly reduced"},{"d":"तुबलम्","m":"army"},{"d":"प्रेक्ष्य","m":"seeing"},{"d":"दैवविपर्ययम्","m":"adversary of god's grace"},{"d":"दृष्टवा","m":"witnessing"},{"d":"अस्य","m":"his"},{"d":"व्यथा","m":"agony"},{"d":"बभूव","m":"experienced"}]},{"v":4,"dev":"उवाच च समीपस्थंमहोदरमरिन्दमम् ।अस्मिन्कालेमहाबाहोजयाशात्वयिमेस्थिता","trans":"And then Ravana spoke to Mahodara who was close by, one who is difficult to encounter, saying \" At this time the hope for my victory is centered in you.\"","words":[{"d":"समीपस्थम्","m":"close by"},{"d":"अरिन्दमम्","m":"difficult to encounter"},{