ng"},{"d":"क्रोधमूर्छितः","m":"deluded with anger"},{"d":"सालम्","m":"sala trees"},{"d":"उत्पाट्य","m":"tearing up"},{"d":"चिक्षेप","m":"shattered"},{"d":"सः","m":"that"},{"d":"नैकधा","m":"one"},{"d":"राक्षसे","m":"on the Rakshasa"},{"d":"रणमूर्दनि","m":"in the battlefield"}]},{"v":16,"dev":"शरैश्चविददारैनंशूरःपरपुरञ्जयः ।स ददर्शततःक्रुद्धःपरिघंपतितंभुवि","trans":"Mahodara, a scourge of enemy forces, who lacerated Sugriva in that manner, angry, made the tree fall on the ground.","words":[{"d":"शूरः","m":"shafts"},{"d":"एनम्","m":"in that way"},{"d":"विददार","m":"lacerated"},{"d":"ततः","m":"them"},{"d":"सः","m":"that"},{"d":"भुवि","m":"ground"},{"d":"पतितम्","m":"fallen"},{"d":"परिघम्","m":"tree"},{"d":"ददर्श","m":"beheld"}]},{"v":17,"dev":"आविध्यतु स तंदीप्तंपरिघंतस्यदर्शयन् ।परिघाग्रेणवेगेनजघानास्यहयोत्तमान् ।6.98.17।।","trans":"Sugriva, picking up that glowing iron bar, exhibiting its top, whirling it around, struck the best of horses of Mahodara.","words":[{"d":"सः","m":"he"},{"d":"दीप्तम्","m":"glowing"},{"d":"तंपरिघम्","m":"that iron bar"},{"d":"आविध्य","m":"failing"},{"d":"तस्य","m":"his"},{"d":"दर्शयन्","m":"exhibiting"},{"d":"उग्रवेगेन","m":"with terrible speed"},{"d":"परिघाग्रेण","m":"top of bar"},{"d":"अस्य","m":"its"},{"d":"हयोत्तमान्","m":"best of horses"},{"d":"जघान","m":"struck"}]},{"v":18,"dev":"तस्माद्धतहयावदीरःसोऽऽवप्लुत्यमहारथात् ।गदांजग्राहसंक्रुद्धोराक्षसोऽऽथमहोदरः","trans":"Then the hero, Mahodara, his horses destroyed, jumped from the great chariot, and took hold of a mace.","words":[{"d":"अथ","m":"and then"},{"d":"वीरः","m":"hero"},{"d":"राक्षसः","m":"Rakshasa"},{"d":"सः","m":"that"},{"d":"हतहयात्","m":"destroyed horses"},{"d":"तस्मात्","m":"from there"},{"d":"महारथात्","m":"great chariot"},{"d":"अवप्लुत्य","m":"jumping down"},{"d":"क्रुद्धः","m":"angry"},{"d":"गदाम्","m":"mace"},{"d":"जग्राह","m":"took hold"}]},{"v":19,"dev":"गदापरिघहस्तौतौयुधिवीरौसमीयतुः ।नर्दन्तौगोवृषप्रख्यौघनाविवसविद्युतौ","trans":"Both the heroes, Mahodara and Sugriva lik